### Admin Login
# @name login
POST http://localhost:8081/api/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get All Routes
GET http://localhost:8081/api/admin/routes
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### Create a Route
POST http://localhost:8081/api/admin/routes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

{
  "origin_city": "Jakarta",
  "origin_pool": "Pool Kebon Jeruk",
  "destination_city": "Bandung",
  "destination_pool": "Pool Pasteur"
}

### Update a Route
# Replace {id} with an actual route ID from the GET response
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/admin/routes/ed488e3c-cc61-47dd-84d8-b81b35e71890
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

{
  "origin_city": "Jakarta",
  "origin_pool": "Pool Kebon Jeruk Baru 2",
  "destination_city": "Bandung",
  "destination_pool": "Pool Pasteur Baru"
}
